text: Csilla Fórián (born 2 January 1969) is a Hungarian badminton player, born in Debrecen. She competed in women's singles and women's doubles at the 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Debrecen Category:Hungarian female badminton players Category:Olympic badminton players of Hungary Category:Badminton players at the 1992 Summer Olympics
